Execution:
----------

./Camera Filename(.obj) yaw pitch roll (camera rotation [rad]) tx ty tz (camera translation [cm]) f (focal length [cm] > 0) cx (X camera principal point [pixels]) cy (Y camera principal point [pixels]) r (pixel/cm) indexes (points indexes file name) width (output image width [pixels]) height (output image height [pixels]) [<output_image.jpg> (output image file name .jpg)]

# Frontal view (e.g)
./Camera <mesh.obj> 0 0 0 0 0 -200 3.5 640 480 400 <point_indexes> 1280 960

# Right lateral view (e.g)
./Camera <mesh.obj> 0 1.5707 0 -200 0 0 3.5 640 480 400 <point_indexes> 1280 960

# Left lateral view (e.g)
./Camera <mesh.obj> 0 -1.5707 0 200 0 0 3.5 640 480 400 <point_indexes> 1280 960


